aria-man-pages (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release of Aria programming language man pages
  * Comprehensive coverage of language features:
    - Type system documentation (int32, string, arrays, structs, etc.)
    - Function documentation (async, sync, closures, etc.)
    - Control flow (if, match, loops, etc.)
    - Memory management (GC, ownership, borrowing)
    - Standard library functions
    - Module system
    - Advanced features
  * 326 man pages covering all language topics
  * Full cross-referencing between related topics
  * Keyword indexing for apropos searches
  * Category-based organization

 -- Aria Language Team <aria@ailp.dev>  Thu, 19 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000
